Oscar-nominated "The Kids Are All Right" trailer
2011-01-30 08:40:50 GMT
Director Lisa Cholodenko's The Kids Are All Right picked up a nom for Best Picture. The critically acclaimed indie film, part comedy and part drama, follows a lesbian couple in Los Angeles raising their two children. When the children's biological father enters back into the picture, the entire family's lives are thrown into disarray.The Kids Are All Right is a 2010 American drama film directed by Lisa Cholodenko and written by Cholodenko and Stuart Blumberg.
